  <summary date="2021-05-10T16:54:06Z" status="Introduced in House">David Dorn Act of 2020

This bill increases criminal penalties for rioting and related acts, such as inciting or organizing a riot.

Specifically, this bill increases the maximum term of imprisonment for such offenses from 5 to 10 years. Additionally, if a fine is imposed for an offense, the bill sets a minimum fine amount of $1,000.</summary>
